Saturday's Calendar under a photo of an Oscar being returned to its original 
owner. 
</P>
</CORRECTION>
<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, Movie fan Bill Kaiser, left, who spent $21,250 to save Lyle Wheeler's 
'59 Oscar from auction, returns it to art director, 84. BRIAN GADBERY / Los 
Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
