<P>
Photo, Photo of Sara Nan Hodges is taped to Sheriff's Department vehicle during 
search, while girl's sister Tisha and friends wait in hopes of a discovery. ; 
Photo, Deputies on horseback search two-square-mile area for girl missing since 
Thursday afternoon. BORIS YARO / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
